## Write a program to store a year in a variable and check whether it is a leap year.

y = 2000

if y % 4 == 0:
    if y % 100 == 0:
        if y % 400 == 0:
            print("leap year")
        else:
            print("not a leap year")
    else:
        print("leap year")
else:
    print("not a leap year")



